==Content==
*This event will be a "what if" operation.
*{{ShipLink|Akagi}} will receive a new remodel.
*It will be possible to encounter new Shimushu-class Kaibokans (DE) during the main operation.
*It will be possible to encounter new Fletcher-class Destroyer (DD) during the extra operation.
*The final reward will be a Colorado-class Battleship.

